{
  "texts": [
    "These advancements pave the way for the (semi-)automation of AD generation, as the crucial steps of generating ADs can be offloaded to these large models with significantly less human involvement.",
    "Figure 2 depicts the components of a typical modern AD generation system with three crucial steps:",
    "Dense Video Captioning (DVC) Given a video, the task is to generate AD scripts that consist of in-formative descriptions.",
    "This inherently multimodal task requires integrating both visual and textual features to create coherent and contextually appropriate AD scripts.",
    "Post-editing (APE) After generating the initial ADs, refine them according to a set of predefined principles."
  ]
}